{"tid":1085821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日就考第一科，好緊張點算好⊙△⊙","createTime":"2019-03-31T12:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T05:17:09.000Z","uid":202348,"like":6,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b34910169b30c65a0f47951416d9bdaf09d43fe6","tid":1085821,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"小妹平時喺學校考開頭5名<br />\n平時都叫做俾心機溫書<br />\n我知道男朋友、老師同屋企人都對我今次公開試有好大期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我亦知道香港既教制係一試定生死，考唔到入大學就同袋底泥無分別，賤過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我從study leave開始就廢寢忘餐咁溫書，為求一張大學入場券。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但一切都喺兩星期前開始有所改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有日我溫書溫到好攰，諗起就嚟考中文oral就覺得頂唔緊，好想搵人傾下心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我男朋友做夜班保安，夜晚掛住做野無聽我電話。<br />\n我一時火遮眼，就down咗個叫tinder既app(我朋友話係交友app嚟) ，搵咗個幾陽光既男仔傾心事...<br />\n<br />\n咁啱個男仔原來都係dse過來人，話可以陪我練oral喎！我見佢咁好人梗係齊約出嚟溫書啦！<br />\n<br />\n點知...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知佢話幫我練習既oral係要我幫佢口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我當時意亂情迷，就幫個賤人口交咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲俾佢中出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我考中文口試嗰時都覺得個口比之前靈活，但係我成個星期未嚟m，於是尋日買咗支驗孕棒check下，原來真係有咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽人講女人大肚會成日嘔㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我聽日考考下想嘔咁點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果考場唔計返時間俾我去嘔，咁我18年嚟既努力咪白費晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2a50b5734b63d3f481fcf9b6f6c4d1c04ff038","tid":1085821,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"Oral sex"},{"pid":"53551d1095573a811838c4c36f3965dd152bc7c0","tid":1085821,"uid":123323,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DdfDpX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DdfDpX.jpg&h=c2019217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都已經返緊工，仲考乜DSE <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7cc328b802bec6534f188c32c34f5cbece960a","tid":1085821,"uid":176650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"帶個紙袋入去咪得囉"},{"pid":"1ca6c4726d7b455d5e7fb3b645b6f61e8de360d4","tid":1085821,"uid":32558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的, 重作啦手足"},{"pid":"34830ef3f810924707a5b3110f6437e1b99e8443","tid":1085821,"uid":23655,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"死獌狗張嘢邊到偷返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31e14f47469f4c2512ca85e567a6f54291c204d","tid":1085821,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"讀ive啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44814273d7e7a45f74af9cbbeab6b0f3ddb72048","tid":1085821,"uid":177089,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"同學你張考證就爛 放咗幾多年？"},{"pid":"99da7fb890d1ee44600359fdfbfbc571ba891da9","tid":1085821,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"成日係馬po見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24b793cb99e6f3e998dff90ff21d028f1f7d6d7","tid":